希望，在我下水前一刻，我感受到了！” 赛后的颁奖仪式上，当现场播报宣布潘展乐获得金牌时，观众爆发出了欢呼声。此外，获得男子100米自由泳第二的澳大利亚选手查尔莫斯在领奖台上也主动伸手与潘展乐互动并表达祝贺。 “自由泳百米之神”潘展乐用一次又一次的优异表现击溃了外界的质疑，也赢得了国外观众和运动员的认可，这一晚的巴黎拉德芳斯体育馆，全世界为潘展乐而欢呼，潘展乐为中国游泳队正名。打招呼被无视、教练被故意溅水，潘展乐：在最难的泳池里一雪前耻-上游新闻 汇聚向上的力量"},"attached_info":"CkAI76Sanp29kPJtEAMaCTEwOTY0MzE2NyCloqu1BjAAOLkNQBpyCTY2MzE0NDIyN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"36 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-073dd4201aa63a82dfdbaf718e55e5f5_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1722536381.349653","card_id":"Q_307115836","target":{"id":307115836,"title":"F16为什么会被定义为空优战机？面对同时代重型空优战机,F16有优势吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/307115836","type":"question","created":1545876279,"answer_count":45,"follower_count":90,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1232,1234,20609,21202,35580],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I76Sanp29kPJtEAMaCDMwNTI0NTExILfmkOEFMAA4WkAbcgkzMDcxMTU4MzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"30 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/c0092f5c9_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1722536381.349818","card_id":"Q_662919153","target":{"id":662919153,"title":"在亲密关系中，我们该如何跟回避型依恋更好相处？「多给空间」是一个好选择吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662919153","type":"question","created":1722253150,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":61,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[404,20818,405458,1388082,3526551],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I76Sanp29kPJtEAMaCTEwOTU5MzIzMCDe/p21BjAAOD1AHHIJNjYyOTE5MTUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"30 万热